'''Karakuni Shrine''' (辛国神社, からくにじんじゃ) is a Shinto shrine located in {{ill|Osaka Prefecture|ja|大阪府|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Fujidera City|ja|藤井寺市|12=draft|12=draft}}. It is classified as a {{ill|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|12=draft|12=draft}}, and its former Rank was that of a {{ill|Murasya|ja|村社|12=draft|12=draft}}.

