* {{ill|Nigihayahi-no-Mikoto|ja|饒速日命|12=draft|12=draft}} (Nigihayahi-no-Mikoto)
* {{ill|Ameno-koyane-no-Mikoto|ja|天児屋根命|1=Ame-no-Koyane|12=draft|12=draft}} (Ameno-koyane-no-Mikoto)
* {{ill|Susanoo-no-Mikoto|ja|素盞鳴命|12=draft|12=draft}} (Susanoo-no-Mikoto)

; Side Hall
* {{ill|Ichikishima-hime-no-Mikoto|ja|市杵島姫命|1=Ichikishima-hime|12=draft|12=draft}} (Ichikishima-hime-no-Mikoto)
* {{ill|Hondawake-no-Mikoto|ja|品陀別命|1=Emperor Ōjin|lt=Hondawake no Mikoto|12=draft|12=draft}} (Hondawake-no-Mikoto)

